<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/felicity-buchan> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Felicity Buchan was Parliamentary Under Secretary of State in the Department for Levelling Up, Housing and Communities between 30 October 2022 and 5 July 2024. She was previously Exchequer Secretary to the Treasury between 7 September 2022 and 28 October 2022."@en .
